Description: AgriDataTools provides a comprehensive collection of statistical,
    biometric, and breeding analysis tools for agricultural research.
    The package supports randomized complete block design (RCBD) analysis,
    variability analysis, genetic parameter estimation, mean comparison,
    correlation analysis, regression analysis, path coefficient analysis,
    principal component analysis, cluster analysis, AMMI analysis,
    GGE biplot analysis, stability analysis, publication-ready tables,
    and graphical visualization for plant breeding, genetics,
    agronomy, horticulture, and crop science experiments.
